blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌咁撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻想拎架車出去大洗一次"},{"pid":"44aae29f7cb8bc8326ab877422a0a5457e0ceaf8","tid":48164,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"weekly"},{"pid":"2bbf195ec9cdb8e23c53e35fdbf2999690358634","tid":48164,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一星期三次 一個月打一次蠟<br />\n<br />\n三百蚊一個月包o黎洗個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你一樣"},{"pid":"9f2dcbc443720a1025f132a29f231951dbc3b97d","tid":48164,"uid":68514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初初買車就一兩星期<br />\n<br />\n揸耐左就幾個月先一次<br />\n<br />\n再耐d就會覺得是撚鳩柒但la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係岩岩有車幾個月<br />\n成日出車前見到雀屎就抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天都還可以既出車前抹下<br />\n夏天咪攪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而冬天太涷唔想洗 又著得多衫阻住"},{"pid":"759211bbf2b3906e1c25f72010b1ab23c6368ff1","tid":48164,"uid":38929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"無定, 鐘意就洗. 呢家好多時因為雀屎樹膠先有衝動去洗<br />\n係有時落完雪唔想比d鹽&quot;啦&quot;爛部車,所以會用水清一清."},{"pid":"9fc89a6b04d573c95175e65e2460617dd86ef616","tid":48164,"uid":55758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"一星期一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ff5176f3b12414ee6c3c1697ecedc9aab65c62","tid":48164,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:01:52.000Z","msg":"兩星期一次，用carpro隻水立方二合一，做埋水鍍膜"},{"pid":"127fd5fae3ee39f86adf636c0e886d3008f386f8","tid":48164,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score